  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_02_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="operation_box ml_0">
            <span class="fraction_box">
              <span>4</span>
              <span>9</span>
            </span>
            &divide;
            <span class="fraction_box">
              <span>2</span>
              <span>9</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          를 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                  <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                    <span>4</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  와
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  는
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  이 각각 몇 개인지 이야기해 보세요.
                </div>
              </div>
              
            </h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <span class="fraction_box ml_0 f32b">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">는</span>
              <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                <span>2</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">이</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span class="f32b">개 이고,</span>
              <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                <span>2</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">는</span>
              <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </span>
              <span class="f32b">이</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span class="f32b">개 입니다.</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                  <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                    <span>4</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  를 그림에 나타내고,
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>4</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  는
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  가 몇 개인지 알아보세요.
                </div>
              </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="boolean_box">
                <span class="tag">예</span>
                <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="4">
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                  <button></button>
                </div>
                <span class="txt txt1">0</span>
                <div class="txt txt2">
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>9</span></span>
                </div>
                <span class="txt txt3" lang="y">1</span>
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span class="f32b">개</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_3">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                    <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  &divide;
                  <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                  </span>
                  는 얼마인가요?
                </div>
              </div>

              
            </h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_4">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                4&divide;2를 이용하여
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>4</span>
                  <span>9</span>
                </span>
                &divide;
                <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>9</span>
                </span>
                를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
              </div>
              </div>
            </h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="col1">
                <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                    <span>4</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                </span>              
                <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>              
                <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>9</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="col2">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span class="f32b">&divide;</span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_5">
            <h3 lang="y">분모가 같은 (분수)&divide;(분수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                    <div class="example_box">
                        <p>분자끼리 나누어 계산합니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <article class="page page_6">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize">
              <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>              
              <div class="summarize_box">
                <span lang="y">분모가 같은 (분수)&divide;(분수)는</span>
                <button class="reveal_btn" lang="y">분자</button>
                <span lang="y" class="small-gap">끼리 나누어 계산합니다.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
